em crowl is the pen name of Eric Crowl who was born on January 2nd, 1986. He is a 3rd year transfer student at UC Davis, majoring in English and minoring in History and Theater. He is actively involved with the editing staff for Nameless Magazine and is also an active Research Fellow for UC Daviss chapter of the Roosevelt Institution (a student run think tank). He also enjoys writing fiction and enjoys reading his work at local open mic events.

More will be coming.
